The generated JSON output is as follows.
<div class="alert alert-dark" role="alert" data-bs-theme="light">
{<br>
"id": 101,<br>
"name": "Laptop",<br>
"price": 15000,<br>
"stock": 25<br>
}
</div>

<h3> Example 2 - Parsing and Displaying JSON Data</h3><br>

