TCLCrypto component is a cryptographic library used for encryption, hashing, and token operations.  
It supports modern algorithms such as AES, SHA-2, SHA-3, and JWT. This component allows developers to configure keys, IVs, output formats, and advanced options for cryptography tasks.  


<div class="table-responsive">
