The <b>TCLProWebBrowser</b> class provides a fully integrated web rendering component for displaying and interacting with web content directly inside Clomosy forms.  
It supports standard web navigation, HTML rendering, JavaScript execution, caching control, and developer debugging tools.  
TCLProWebBrowser allows you to embed modern web experiences within your Clomosy applications while maintaining control through the native component interface.

<div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
{| class="infobox" style="width: 100%; border: 1px solid #007bff; background-color: #e6f7ff; border-radius: 5px; padding: 15px; border-collapse: separate;"
| style="font-weight: bold; color: #007bff; padding-bottom: 5px;" | Information: Integrated Web Rendering
|-
| The TclProWebBrowser component enables loading of remote or local HTML content, executing JavaScript code, and managing browser history within Clomosy UI forms.
|-
| Example:  <code>ProWebBrowser.Navigate('https://cms.clomosy.com')</code>
|}
</div>

<div class="table-responsive" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
{| class="wikitable" style="border: 2px solid #c3d7e0; width:100%"
! style="background-color: #c3d7e0"| Feature
! style="background-color: #c3d7e0"| Use of
! style="background-color: #c3d7e0"| Definition
|-
