The <b>TclShareService</b> class allows you to share files, images, or text content directly using the native sharing features of the device.  
It provides a simple way to integrate content sharing functions (such as sharing a document, CSV file, or text) in Clomosy applications with full Android and iOS support. <br>

<span style="color:blue"><b>TclShareService</b></span> : A component that enables sharing of files, images, or text through the system's default share dialog.<br>
<br>

<div class="alert alert-info" role="alert" data-bs-theme="light">
<b>Note:</b> TclShareService is available on <b>Android</b> and <b>iOS</b> platforms.  
On both systems, it uses the native share dialog to ensure a seamless user experience.
</div>

